{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330300/extras/Title_\u82f1\u6587.png?t=1731561040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a turn-based battle game in a 2D cartoon style set against the backdrop of future space warfare. Players take on the role of a spaceship captain, continuously improving their spaceship's construction and defending against invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330300/extras/\u6807\u9898_\u4fdd\u62a4\u98de\u8239EN.png?t=1731561040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal of the game is to protect your starship's core from being destroyed by enemies and destroy the enemy's core.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330300/extras/\u4fdd\u62a4\u98de\u8239\u7d20\u6750.gif?t=1731561040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330300/extras/\u6807\u9898_\u8d2d\u4e70\u6b66\u5668EN.png?t=1731561040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the shop, purchase and craft more advanced equipment to enhance the starship's combat power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330300/extras/\u5408\u6210\u88c5\u5907\u7d20\u6750.gif?t=1731561040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330300/extras/\u6807\u9898_\u5236\u5b9a\u7b56\u7565EN.png?t=1731561040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose the right equipment, formulate a strategy, place them in the optimal positions, and prepare for the upcoming battle!</p><p class=\"bb_para